"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-01-Check-out-the-best-swimmer-and-relay-team-on-August-1-at-Paris-2024-1vIkxSrnCpy-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  A total of 18 golds are up for grabs on Thursday at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics. The competitions in the following four events may be worth your attention.  The artistic gymnastics women's all-round final will take place at the Bercy Arena at 18:15 (GMT+2). Qiu Qiyuan and Ou Yushan of China will be among the competitors.  The fencing women's foil team final is scheduled to get underway at the Grand Palais at 19:10 (GMT+2).  And two exciting swimming finals will be held in the Olympic Aquatics Centre at the Paris La Defense Arena, first the women's 200-meter butterfly event at 20:30 (GMT+2), and later the women's 4\\u00c3\\u0097200-meter freestyle relay at 22:03 (GMT+2).  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"